divs: Sighting Detailsout 2-3am 3miles south of city lights in farm land. trying my new orion scope. no sound but windy bright moon & stars. the ufo? came from the west over me to the east. No sound very low to ground. This is the 1st time I have told anyone other than my wife. I was alone & I also just sent this info to coast to coast but I don't know if there interested. I don't take drugs & i'm very open to anything. Derreck
